---
title: Veggie Mince Shepherd's Pie with Cheesy Mash Top & Mixed Leaf Salad
description: A vegetarian dinner that’s comfort food at its best? Sign us up! This richly spiced veggie mince and tomato base gets a golden
potato topping and piles of melted, oozy cheese for a hearty bake that will warm you up from the inside out.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/veggie-mince-shepherd-pie-0104da4f.jpg
